          &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;item&#34; title=&#34;samwhelp&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl image&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9zYW13aGVscC5naXRodWIuaW8vbm90ZS1hYm91dC12aW0vcmVhZC9saW5rLmh0bWw=&#34; data-background-image=&#34;/assets/404.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
          &lt;div class=&#34;info&#34;&gt;
          &lt;span class=&#34;exturl title&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9zYW13aGVscC5naXRodWIuaW8vbm90ZS1hYm91dC12aW0vcmVhZC9saW5rLmh0bWw=&#34;&gt;vim 的操作 2&lt;/span&gt;
          &lt;p class=&#34;desc&#34;&gt;裡面有關於vim 的設定參考。&lt;/p&gt;
